2) Write a Python program to accept two strings and find common characters 
between the two strings also check whether both strings are equal or not.

str1 = input("Enter first string: ")
str2 = input("Enter second string: ")
common = set(str1) & set(str2)
print("Common characters between the two strings:", common)
if str1 == str2:
 print("Both strings are equal")
else:
